item.title: Giant Squid may steal the spotlight in 2016 with underwater beaut Abzu
item.description:
Giant Squid may steal the spotlight in 2016 with underwater beaut Abzu

The video game industry has continued to introduce amazing new IP after amazing new IP and we could have yet another one on our hands in the form of Abzu. From developers who worked on the smash-hit Journey comes a new tale that takes place not on land, but underwater.

item.title: To Azimuth
item.description:
To Azimuth

Announcement trailer for To Azimuth, a narrative-driven alien abduction mystery following two siblings as they search for their brother in the humid haze of 1970's Alabama. From the creator of Three Fourths Home: Extended Edition.
